snippet.title: Go Full Tilt - Fortnite OG Chapter 1 Season 2 is Live!
snippet.description:
Grab your Glider and jump off the Battle Bus as Fortnite OG enters Chapter 1 Season 2, bringing back beloved POIs, like Tilted Towers, as well as legendary loot and more! 

https://fn.gg/FortniteOGSeason2

An all-new OG Pass is also here based on the classic Chapter 1 Season 2. Unlock items inspired by Sparkle Specialist, Black Knight, and Cuddle Team Leader. To claim the premium rewards as you earn XP, purchase the OG Pass for only 1,000 V-Bucks or get it through Fortnite Crew! 

This Season’s OG Pass also has an unlockable alt Style for each Outfit, and for many of the accessories! The Pass will be available to progress in until the Season ends March 25, 2025.
